{"tid":2213413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中五女生流淚拜祭：希望彥霖安息】","createTime":"2020-09-22T13:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T15:41:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"622bdabc9ec40ad80c5a8d876d1c8a82880c5c5f","tid":2213413,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p640x640/119949018_1268749606801779_3250075180850020459_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=C0dV-rLO-K0AX8oZHi3&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=906820f73818ccb73fc9abcb475b65e8&amp;oe=5F8FB059\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp640x640%2F119949018_1268749606801779_3250075180850020459_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DC0dV-rLO-K0AX8oZHi3%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26tp%3D6%26oh%3D906820f73818ccb73fc9abcb475b65e8%26oe%3D5F8FB059&h=d9acaedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾新聞 &middot; 1 hr &middot; <br />\n <br />\n【中五女生流淚拜祭：希望彥霖安息】中五的A同學，去年10月受社會事件影響，情緒病復發。她指，進食藥物後情緒容易波動 ，今日本不打算到祭壇拜祭。不過，放學回家時經過知專設計學院，卻忍不住停下腳步，認為「都行到呢到無可能唔拜祭」，但未走到壇前，便已流下眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n剛剛放學，A同學仍背著一個粉紅色的大背包，手中緊抱著湖水綠色的電腦袋，又拜托同樣前往拜祭的路人，為她先看管貴重物品，好讓她能上前獻花。被問到是否信服死因裁決的結果，她雙眼一眨，指自己已對政權失去信心，亦對死因裁判不抱期望，只能相信「人在做、天在看」，希望彥霖能安息。<br />\n<br />\n攝影：周滿鏗<br />\n<br />\n【恰巧不是你家女兒 專頁重整「彥霖之死」】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3c1V6gK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3c1V6gK&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=74e21582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3c1V6gK</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n亼 緊貼眾新聞 亼<br />\nFollow TG：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkcnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcnews&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=bb25773d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkcnews</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zykNXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zykNXc&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=98f6b7e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zykNXc</a><br />\n<br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37AfYcp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37AfYcp&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=2c0d38bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37AfYcp</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37A1PMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37A1PMI&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=104add8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37A1PMI</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n現在訂閱眾新聞一年或以上，送柳俊江新書《元朗黑夜 ── 我的記憶和眾人的記憶》或譚蕙芸新書《天愈黑，星愈亮 ── 反修例運動的人和事》，二選一：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/訂閲我們\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F%E8%A8%82%E9%96%B2%E6%88%91%E5%80%91&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=1b7d8f96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/訂閲我們</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1268749596801780/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fphotos%2Fa.384058221937593%2F1268749596801780%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=3ebfcd26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1268749596801780/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"8a77ed8fe134d097442d176e4b49cce5442a42cf","tid":2213413,"uid":65888,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21596f0eaef163b66a4f2d3a850ea66b7236b841","tid":2213413,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a77ed8fe134d097442d176e4b49cce5442a42cf","tid":2213413,"uid":65888,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:32:16